name: Lee Young-ji
description: '''Lee Young-ji''' ({{Korean|hangul=이영지}}; born September 10, 2002) is a South Korean rapper. She is the winner of ''[[High School Rapper (season 3)|High School Rapper 3]]'' and ''[[Show Me the Money 11]]'' as well as the host of the web talk show ''Not Much Prepared''. She released her first extended play ''[[16 Fantasy]]'' on June 21, 2024.
